name: V Nixie Painting #1
description: I'm going to mint one NFT per week of one of my stencil art pieces. While I am for the most part a photographer, I do sometimes use my own photos to create stencils which I then spray paint onto canvas. Each of these will be a 1/1 edition of a unique physical painting that lives somewhere out there in the real world. I used some of my stencils multiple times but each painting was a unique color scheme and the stencil painting process itself created a one of a kind  painting each time a stencil was used. In the future there will be one more version of this stencil minted.
